After reading many of the reviews for this hotel and others in Vancouver we decided to stay at the Wedgewood.	When we come back to Vancouver in the future, we would definately stay at the Wedgewood again!	We look forward to our next stay at this wonderful hotel.	My husband and I just returned from a stay at the Wedgewood for our honeymoon.	We chose to stay here for our first few nights in Canada on our honeymoon.	Other than that we loved our stay and will return when we stay in Vancouver in the future.	We thoroughly enjoyed our stay and would highly recommend this hotel.